summary: This is a deed transferring property at 9 East 71st Street, New York, NY from Birch Wathen School, Inc. to Nine East 71st Street Corporation. The deed is executed pursuant to a New York Supreme Court order from February 6, 1989. The document includes notarizations and recording information.

keyFacts: The property at 9 East 71st Street, New York, NY was transferred from Birch Wathen School, Inc. to Nine East 71st Street Corporation.
The transfer was executed pursuant to a New York Supreme Court Order dated February 6, 1989 (index No. 2225/89).
The document is a formal deed describing the land parcel (50 feet by 102 feet 2 inches) in detail.
The deed includes covenants related to lien law compliance, indicating the consideration was to be held as a trust fund to pay for improvements.
The document was recorded in New York County, with the return address for the recorded copy being attorney Jack S. Levey in Columbus, Ohio.
